melts of a graphite-saturated eclogite. Furthermore, calculations suggest that eclogite can remain saturated in graphite in the convecting upper mantle, acting as a reservoir for C.},
	language = {en},
	number = {2},
	urldate = {2021-04-13},
	journal = {Contributions to Mineralogy and Petrology},
	author = {Eguchi, James and Dasgupta, Rajdeep},
